metadata.name: Pink Goop Skull
metadata.description:
I wanted to make something a little brighter for my skull arts, and here it is.

Getting the fluid simulation on this one was hard! and took ages to process but it was worth it in my opinion.

The vibe I am trying to portray here is a sense of goofiness, my skull arts are commonly dark and don't touch the happiness emotions and here is my adaptation of a more brighter theme compared to my others

[Check out the entire collection](https://www.pleysiertom.com/skull-art)
